data.description: Welcome home! This wonderful 3-bedroom home with a 2-car garage, offers the perfect blend of comfort, and functionality. Nestled in a highly sought after Carson City neighborhood that resides within close proximity to restaurants, shopping, parks, entertainment and a short drive to Lake Tahoe and Reno. This home boasts 1536 square feet of open concept living, with a formal livingroom that features a fireplace, and a separate great room. This home is sure to please! This home has a newer roof and exterior paint.
